title: Relaunch
body:
If Opensea doesn't respond within 48 hours commence work on relaunching the project and airdropping the new version to holders 1:1.  Relaunch would entail:

1. New art, suggest pixels but keep the cat theme.  Hire a pixel artist to rip these out.
2. New contract, this time remove all references to other projects make it unique to us.
3. New name and website, from scratch no copy pasta.
4. Refrain from any talk of rewards or financial incentive, utility only.
5. Transfer all assets from the multisig into a new one.
author: 0xD7ed008295E7dDD477A557E7646525E2CDFBb9BE
